itemDescription: divorced first wife of Henry Dundas, 1st Viscount Melville (1751-1843)

wikipedia_page.main: Elizabeth Rannie, also known as Elizabeth Rennie, (1750–1847) was a Scottish noblewoman who was married to Henry Dundas, 1st Viscount Melville, and was mother to Robert Dundas, 2nd Viscount Melville.
